{"tid":1769022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大學擴建撤回］政府向立法會申請18.6億興建機場警區基地","createTime":"2019-12-04T13:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T12:38:11.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"61da1679dbb71966ae332feafbfbd2c35c6722dd","tid":1769022,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T13:33:04.000Z","msg":"政府向立法會申請逾50億元，興建機場第三條跑道相關設施，當中18.6億元會用於興建機場警區行動基地，以及改建現時的機場警署，預計2024年落成。<br />\n<br />\n政府指，隨著三跑道系統的發展，機場面積將擴大約 650 公頃，預計2030年，旅客數目會增至每年一億人次，對警務需求將會大增。政府又指，機場面對恐襲的風險不容忽視，只靠現時的機場警署，將難以應付警務需求的增長，故須額外興建全新的行動基地。<br />\n<br />\n其他計劃興建的設施，包括出入境檢查站、衞生署和漁護署的辦公大樓、航空氣象系統等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3029675630473806?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3029675630473806%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e5Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=735b9e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3029675630473806?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"724ee09d79f258485c379aa9071a5fa17ab77678","tid":1769022,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"75230343c28ad85ae6b44b5ce70bd22ec66df21a","tid":1769022,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T13:44:25.000Z","msg":"起個站崗咪得，洗唔洗十幾億呀"},{"pid":"5d68f336ff20d096fb76c3c6ca7262e136fb0681","tid":1769022,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T14:06:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a04011f4253f3f492d14b5a893fea3f68a07e7f0","tid":1769022,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.